# DNS Incident Report – Network Traffic Analysis

## Description

This incident report was completed as part of the Google Cybersecurity Professional Certificate.

The objective of this activity was to analyze network traffic using tcpdump, identify the affected protocols, determine the root cause of the issue, and document the incident following cybersecurity reporting best practices.

**Skills demonstrated**
- DNS
- ICMP
- UDP
- Network Traffic Analysis
- tcpdump
- Incident Documentation
